"""
Face Animation Transfer Tool — lion:face_main_ctrl
====================================================
Exports and imports all facial blend shape keyframe data
from a single control node across Maya scenes.

Usage:
    # In SOURCE scene:
    export_face_anim(file_path="C:/anim/face_anim.json")

    # In TARGET scene:
    import_face_anim(file_path="C:/anim/face_anim.json")

    # Or launch the UI:
    launch_ui()
"""

